I'm really glad to hear that this article helped your reduce your WordPress load time! I wrote another general &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.inmotionhosting.com/support/website/wordpress/how-to-optimize-wordpress&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;optimize WordPress guide&lt;/a&gt; that you might want to glance over as well to reduce your load time even further.<br />
